---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Grandevity | Interactive Studio & Digital Solutions">
  <main>
    <header class="hero">
      <h1>Engineering <span class="text-gradient">Digital Worlds</span></h1>
      <p>Grandevity is a multi-disciplinary studio building original interactive experiences and providing elite digital, financial, and strategic consulting for modern businesses.</p>
    </header>

    <section id="games" class="section-container">
      <h2>In-House IP</h2>
      <div class="card-grid single">
        <div class="card game-card">
          <div class="game-image-placeholder">
            <span>[ Classified Concept Art ]</span>
          </div>
          <div class="card-content">
            <h3>Project: Kiwi <span style="font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: normal; color: #94a3b8;">(Working Title)</span></h3>
            <span class="badge">In Active Development</span>
            <p>An unannounced, original web game project exploring a unique Kiwi theme. Currently in the engineering and prototyping phase. More details to come as development progresses.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="services" class="section-container">
      <h2>Studio Services</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Fueling our creative engines through high-level B2B partnerships.</p>
      
      <div class="card-grid">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Digital & Web Services</h3>
          <p>Development, maintenance, and hosting of robust digital storefronts, web tools, and content platforms.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Business Consulting</h3>
          <p>Strategic advisory and process consulting to help independent businesses optimize their operational workflows.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Financial Bookkeeping</h3>
          <p>Preparation of financial records and ledger reconciliation, ensuring absolute precision and compliance.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Systems & ERP Architecture</h3>
          <p>Custom ERP solution design and implementation, bridging the gap between financial data and operational tech.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  main {
    padding: 0 5%;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 6rem 0;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 4rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .text-gradient {
    background-image: linear-gradient(45deg, #38bdf8, #818cf8);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-size: 400%;
    background-position: 0%;
  }

  .hero p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: #94a3b8;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .section-container {
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    color: #94a3b8;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .card-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .card-grid.single {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .card {
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: transform 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
  }

  .card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    border-color: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.5);
  }

  .card-content {
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .card h3 {
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  .card p {
    color: #94a3b8;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .game-image-placeholder {
    width: 100%;
    height: 300px;
    background: #0f172a;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: #475569;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
  }

  .badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.1);
    color: #38bdf8;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
</style>